Add the Mflix Collections as Data Sources
-----------------------------------------

Once the load operation completes, you can add the collections
containing the sample data as :doc:`data sources </data-sources>` in
|charts-short|. Adding a collection as a data source links the
collection to |charts-short| and allows you to visualize that data.

.. include:: /includes/steps/add-data-source-mflix.rst

Next Steps
----------

Now that you have established the data source in |charts-short|, you
can :ref:`Create a New Dashboard <movie-data-new-dash>` which will
hold the visualizations.
